response.overview: The Shrimpskins, Slim and Wally, watch a Sofa Ranch commercial and want to trade in their couch for a new one so they can win a fun weekend with the craziest people in the world. The Shrimpskins' couch won't fit through their door until Wally chainsaws the couch into little pieces and mails them individually. The Sloper family wins the competition, but the Shrimpskins are named the craziest people in the world. The Shrimpskins celebrate until the family arrives and they block off the door.
response.title: We Are The Shrimpskins
